inquiries.query:
SELECT 
	job_id, 
	job_title_short, 
	job_location, 
	job_via, 
	salary_year_avg
FROM 
	job_postings_fact
WHERE 
	(
    (job_title_short = 'Data Analyst' AND salary_year_avg > 100000)
    OR 
	(job_title_short = 'Business Analyst' AND salary_year_avg > 70000)
    )
AND 
	(job_location = 'Boston, MA' OR	job_location = 'Anywhere')

-- by Luke
